                            description: "This classic Irish soda bread, adapted from Darina Allen, offers a taste of Ireland with its simple yet delightful flavor. Perfect when served fresh from the oven and slathered with good salted Irish butter, this bread is an excellent side for corned beef and cabbage or enjoyable on its own any time of the year.",
